{"parse":{"title":"Colour Filter","pageid":541,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>2-2-200</b>\n</p><p>Alternative term: (Colour) Shade (<span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"dfcf28d0734569a6a693bc8194de62bf\">G</span>.<span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"9d5ed678fe57bcca610140957afab571\">B</span>.)\n</p><p><span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"7fc56270e7a70fa81a5935b72eacbe29\">A</span> selective filter, usually of glass or plastic, producing a change of colour in the transmitted light.\n</p><p><span class=\"mw-image-border\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:Angle_Of_Uncertainty_2023.png\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/9/95/Angle_Of_Uncertainty_2023.png/400px-Angle_Of_Uncertainty_2023.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"400\" height=\"296\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/9/95/Angle_Of_Uncertainty_2023.png/600px-Angle_Of_Uncertainty_2023.png 1.5x, /wiki/dictionary/images/9/95/Angle_Of_Uncertainty_2023.png 2x\"></a></span>\n</p><p><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<i>Please note that this is the term as it stands in the original <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"0a1217bfe27a54fc7e55b72fc62c2371\">IALA</span> Dictionary edition (1970-1989)</i>\n<br>\n</p>\n<div class=\"LanguageLinks\">\n<table width=\"100%\">\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\" style=\"background: #FFFFFF\">\n<td style=\"width: 25px; padding-left: 0em; border-right: 1px solid #aaaaaa;border-left: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-top: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-bottom: 1px solid #EEF3E2;\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:25px-Geographylogo.png\" class=\"mw-file-description\" title=\"Languages\"><img alt=\"Languages\" src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/8/82/25px-Geographylogo.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></a></span></td>\n<td style=\"padding: 1px 1em 0; background: #EEF3E2;\">\n<p><b><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">English</a></b>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"dfcf28d0734569a6a693bc8194de62bf\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>centre of gravity\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"9d5ed678fe57bcca610140957afab571\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Centre of buoyancy\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"7fc56270e7a70fa81a5935b72eacbe29\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>ampere\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"0a1217bfe27a54fc7e55b72fc62c2371\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>International Association of Marine Aids to Navigation and Lighthouse Authorities - AISM\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260615093739\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.034 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.042 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 60/1000000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 766/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 177/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/100\nExpensive parser function count: 4/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   12.274      1 -total\n 75.26%    9.238      1 Template:Languages\n 51.08%    6.269      4 Template:Languages/Lang\n 23.73%    2.912      1 Template:IALAFooter\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key wiki_iala_dictionary_1_41:pcache:idhash:541-0!canonical and timestamp 20260615093739 and revision id 10289. Ren